    "name": "Baker Business 3 - Halloween Pack",
    "steam_appid": 2219460,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219460/extras/0668fd0ffcb8fb241a85c13cdbaf4e23.avif?t=1679787223\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>Halloween is coming to your bakery! Embrace all the spooky and cute things autumn has to offer this time of year. Put out jack-o-lanterns and candy bowls for Halloween and bake pumpkin bread muffins for fall.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219460/extras/262a8b0f5a991fa74f67986b3ee4a918.avif?t=1679787223\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>Get your bakery ready in time for the influx of trick or treaters—I mean customers—you're about to receive! Put up bats, banners, spiders, candy cutouts and more to make your shop the spookiest in town.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219460/extras/3033401a5cc3d956cff1b98b2c8dba6f.avif?t=1679787223\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>Discover all the fun Halloween baked goods from creepy cupcakes, sweet sugar cookies, scary-good cakes, festive donuts and so much more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219460/extras/bd846bc50074de3273670d4741312504.avif?t=1679787223\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>As you bake and sell festive recipes you'll earn 'Halloween Tickets' that you can collect and spend in the Halloween Shop.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219460/extras/3e5178a10caa498bfa79e58dd0ca2aa3.avif?t=1679787223\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>Spend your tickets to unlock Halloween recipes, pumpkins, candy bowls and wallpapers!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219460/extras/c6166e7f73324a36fc9177e8ec1ba50d.avif?t=1679787223\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>Put out a refillable candy bowl for your customers to spread the Halloween spirit! Choose between 4 spooky and fun designs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219460/extras/e70a3d32d14ebc8b6dbdb88a078f7cfb.avif?t=1679787223\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>You can't make caramel apples without the melted caramel! Play with seasonal ingredients including pumpkin puree, candy corn, craft supplies (for spooky cakes of course!), caramel pieces, and spooky sprinkles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219460/extras/541a00c7165765a485897a26db392315.avif?t=1679787223\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>Included in the Halloween pack is a collection of autumn themed banners, cutouts, and of course recipes to bake!",
